---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms of Use — ytomp3 Converter"
  description="Terms of Use for ytomp3.in. Understand your rights and limitations when using our YouTube converter."
  canonicalUrl="https://ytomp3.in/terms-of-use"
>
  <Navbar />
  
  <main class="flex-grow">
    <!-- Header -->
    <section class="py-12 bg-canvas border-b border-hairline" aria-label="Terms of Use Header">
      <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-mute mb-2">Legal Documents</p>
        <h1 class="display-lg text-primary text-4xl mb-2">Terms of Use.</h1>
        <p class="text-xs font-mono text-mute">Last Updated: May 31, 2026</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Content -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-canvas-soft" aria-label="Terms of Use Content">
      <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="prose prose-sm max-w-none text-body space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Welcome to <strong class="text-primary">ytomp3.in</strong>. By accessing or using our website, you agree to comply with and be bound by the following Terms of Use. Please review these terms carefully before converting links.
          </p>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-primary">1. Acceptable Use of the Service</h2>
            <p>
              ytomp3.in is designed to function as a technical converter utility. It allows users to download and transcode online media files to offline containers.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
              <li><strong>Personal Use Only:</strong> Our service is provided strictly for personal, non-commercial use.</li>
              <li><strong>Copyrighted Content:</strong> You are responsible for ensuring that you have the legal right or permission from the content owner before converting and downloading any video. We do not host, store, or index any media files on our servers.</li>
              <li><strong>System Integrity:</strong> You agree not to use automated tools, bots, or scripts to access our conversion backend or spam our nodes. Doing so will result in an immediate IP address ban.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-primary">2. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
            <p>
              The design layout, code codebase, brand mark, styling assets, logos, and custom graphics of ytomp3.in are protected by copyright and intellectual property laws. We do not claim ownership of the media files converted through our platform; all trademarks, logos, and content titles belong to their respective copyright holders.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-primary">3. Disclaimer of Warranties</h2>
            <p>
              THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. WE DO NOT GUARANTEE THAT THE SERVICE WILL BE UNINTERRUPTED, SECURE, ACCURATE, OR FREE OF ERRORS. WE ARE NOT LIABLE FOR ACTIONS TAKEN BY THIRD-PARTY STREAM SITES THAT INTERFERE WITH THE CONVERSION CAPABILITIES.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-primary">4. Limitation of Liability</h2>
            <p>
              IN NO EVENT SHALL RYTOMP3.IN, ITS OWNERS, ADMINISTRATORS, OR DEVELOPERS BE LIABLE FOR ANY DIRECT, INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, OR CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES ARISING OUT OF THE USE OF OR INABILITY TO USE THE SERVICE. YOU AGREE TO DEFEND, INDEMNIFY, AND HOLD US HARMLESS FROM ANY CLAIMS RESULTING FROM YOUR USAGE.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-primary">5. Termination</h2>
            <p>
              We reserve the right to suspend or block access to the service for any user or IP address at our sole discretion, without notice, for violating these terms.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="space-y-3">
            <h2 class="text-base font-semibold text-primary">6. Contact</h2>
            <p>
              For inquiries regarding these Terms of Use, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@ytomp3.in" class="text-link hover:underline font-mono">support@ytomp3.in</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
